rows.label: tlk42300023_03_msg0001
rows.name:
No matter how much Avaritia
develop, Twelve Brothersisterpon
never get better selection of products!

rows.label: tlk42300023_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Motata say that not happen until other
11 brothersisterpon come back from
resource-finding mission!

rows.label: tlk42300023_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Heard on grape-melonvine that they
went to Invidia, Mor Superbian and some
other place never heard of in life.

rows.label: tlk42300023_03_msg0004
rows.name:
But Motata also say they probably not
ever come back unless someone go to
fetch them...
